{{Infobox film | name = Trilogia das novas familias | image = | caption = | director = Isabel Noronha | producer = Ebano Multimedia | writer = | starring = | distributor = | released = 2008 | runtime = 45 minutes | country = [[Mozambique]] | language = | budget = | gross = | screenplay = | cinematography = Karl Sousa | editing = Orlando Mesquita | music = }}
'''''Trilogia das novas familias''''' is a 2008 documentary film.
== Synopsis == The film consists of three short documentary films that show the faces and give voices to children orphaned by [[AIDS]]. The intentions of the documentary are to focus attention on the dismemberment of families in [[Mozambique]] due to AIDS, because it is a harsh reality and too often ignored.
